Drupal module for client:
- Example of Drupal batch setup
- URL assignment to nodes
- Batch script reads external page and parses it using simple DOM, strips data from the page and saves it to Drupal
- Batch script scans page for images and saves them into website files folder based on the node
- Good example of how properly save image as a file, them purpose and the attach it to the node